ere ranked no six on vanity fair’s  new establishment list no  on cnet’s  most influential investors list and no  and  respectively on the  forbes midas list of tech’s top investors in april  andreessen and andreessen horowitz general partners ben horowitz peter levine jeff jordan john o’farrell and scott weiss pledged to donate half of their lifetime incomes from venture capital to charitable organizations in  andreessen was named in the time  an annual list of the  most influential people in the world assembled by time in  andreessen was one of five internet and web pioneers awarded the inaugural queen elizabeth prize for engineering current venturesedit andreessen cofounded and was chairman of ning the third company he established after netscape and loudcloud in september  it was announced that ning had been sold to mode media for a reported price of  million andreessen joined glam media’s board of directors following the sale andreessen is an investor in social news website digg and several other technology startups such as plazes netvibes casttv twitter and the rockmelt browser launched in  he is a personal investor in such diverse companies as linkedin and boutique bank raine andreessen serves on the board of facebook ebay hewlett packard enterprise kno stanford hospital bump technologies anki oculus vr dialpad and tinyco he serves as advisor to asana and director of collabnet andreessen is a proponent of bitcoin and cryptocurrency and has described the technology as innovative and radical his venture capital firm andreessen horowitz has invested more than  million in bitcoinrelated startups as of july   personal lifeedit andreessen married laura arrillaga in  she is the founder of the silicon valley social venture fund and daughter of silicon valley real estate billionaire john arrillaga in  andreessen expressed some support for republican candidate mitt romney during the  primary season he endorsed republican candidate carly fiorina but after fiorina dropped out of the race andreessen switched his endorsement to the democratic nominee hillary clinton citing the republican nominee donald trumps antiimmigration stance criticismedit in february  marc andreessen posted a tweet in response to indias decision to apply net neutrality to facebooks proposed project free basics the tweet suggested that anticolonialism had been catastrophic for the indian people andreessen later deleted the tweet following criticism from indians and nonindians alike including facebook founder mark zuckerberg facebook spent millions advertising free basics to the indian public the project failed due to violations setting preferential tariffs in accessing content and setting up a walled garden on the internet referencesedit  the worlds billionaires list forbes retrieved may     tad friend may   tomorrow’s advance man  marc andreessen’s plan to win the future   edgar online  marc lowell andreessen  sec filings googlebrandedgaronlinecom  retrieved    a b dan frommer marc andreessen joins facebook board alleyinsidercom retrieved    facebook newsroom   investorebaycom  baldwin clare  hp snags web pioneer andreessen for board reuters   robert cailliau may  www awards cern retrieved    the worldwide web hall of fame best of the web directory  retrieved    a b simone payment marc andreessen and jim clark the founders of netscape the rosen publishing group  p  isbn   marc andreessen and jim clark the founders of netscape  simone payment  google books retrieved  – via google books   marc l andreessen engineering at illinois university of illinois at urbanachampaign retrieved  march    roads and crossroads of internet history chapter  birth of the web   in  ken mccarthy held the first conference to discuss the commercial prospects available on the internet and internet marketing as a direct marketing medium  netscapes marc andreessen time magazine    at just  he appearedbarefoot and wearing a crownon the cover of time steve hamm  the education of marc andree