book ebay and hp among others andreessen is a frequent keynote speaker and guest at silicon valley conferences he is one of only six inductees in the world wide web hall of fame announced at the first international conference on the world wide web in andreessen was born in cedar falls iowa and raised in new lisbon wisconsin the son of patricia and lowell andreessen who worked for a seed company he received his bachelors degree in computer science from the university of illread more about marc andreesen product market fitmarc andreessen latest news innovation is as much about finding partners as building products leading vcs like andreessen horowitz and khosla ventures are shifting their focus to help connect startups with innovative ceos marc andreessen has long been calling for greater collaboration and now has a small army of people focused on helping startups  posted july    am software is helping the world not just eating it infor ceo on vertical cloud is this drilling down to specific problems what entrepreneur and investor marc andreessen meant when he said “software is eating the world” “maybe ‘it’s helping the world’ might be a better way to put it” said charles phillips pictured  posted july    am why universal basic income is gaining support critics facebook cofounder chris hughes venture capitalist marc andreessen and y combinator president sam altman have all said it’s worth exploring y combinator’s nonprofit research lab started a basic income pilot with fewer than  people in oakland last  posted july    pm marc andreessen just gave loads of advice to startup founders marc andreessen says introductions are vital and to give vcs three to four months to complete an investment its a great time for experienced founders as startups are taking on big incumbents directly which requires experience andreessen delivered  posted july    am quick notes from marc andreessen’s ama stripe has an excellent post up titled marc andreessen answers questions from stripe at